Mor'du or not, I'll avenge your mother!

902
01:12:21,212 --> 01:12:25,171
I'll not risk losing you, too.
Merida: No, dad! Just listen to me.

903
01:12:25,258 --> 01:12:27,920
Listen! You can't!

904
01:12:27,969 --> 01:12:32,303
It's your wife Elinor!
Maudie, keep this and don't let her out.

905
01:12:32,431 --> 01:12:34,843
What about the bear?
Just stay put.

906
01:12:37,645 --> 01:12:39,761
Oh...

907
01:13:02,128 --> 01:13:04,790
Come on, you sorry bunch of galoots!
Yah!

908
01:13:13,681 --> 01:13:15,046
Mum!

909
01:13:15,141 --> 01:13:16,722
No.

910
01:13:16,809 --> 01:13:18,345
No. Mum.

911
01:13:40,499 --> 01:13:41,909
Maudie. Maudie!

912
01:13:42,001 --> 01:13:44,663
I need youl!

913
01:13:44,712 --> 01:13:46,168
Now!

914
01:13:49,175 --> 01:13:51,791
Oh, no.

915
01:13:53,179 --> 01:13:55,090
Maudie.

916
01:14:00,811 --> 01:14:01,846
Get the key.

917
01:14:17,536 --> 01:14:18,571
Yah!

918
