Oh, Maudie!

919
01:14:29,674 --> 01:14:32,211
Needle and thread. Needle and thread.
Needle and thread.

920
01:14:50,444 --> 01:14:52,059
There he goes!

921
01:14:52,154 --> 01:14:54,816
Needle and thread.
Needle and thread. Needle and thread.

922
01:14:54,907 --> 01:14:56,147
Ah, you beauty!

923
01:15:22,977 --> 01:15:26,185
One, two... huh?

924
01:15:30,109 --> 01:15:31,940
_maudie: Oh!

925
01:15:55,509 --> 01:15:57,591
Steady, Hamish.

926
01:15:57,636 --> 01:15:59,627
Fergus: There he goes.

927
01:16:09,774 --> 01:16:11,765
Fergus: We've got his track!

928
01:16:16,530 --> 01:16:18,691
Back, back, back!
Get him!

929
01:16:22,620 --> 01:16:24,611
Angus! Easy, laddie.

930
01:16:28,375 --> 01:16:29,990
Hubert, Harris, help Hamish.

931
01:16:31,253 --> 01:16:33,853
Fergus: Watch your blade!
You're going to take somebody's arm off!

932
01:16:34,673 --> 01:16:36,004
Aye, we've got you now!

933
01:16:37,843 --> 01:16:40,489
Fergus: Give me a hand over here!
Put your back into it, Dingwall!

934
01:16:40,513 --> 01:16:41,698
Lord Dingwall:
I'm doing all the pulling here.

935
01:16:41,722 --> 01:16:43,402
Lord macguffin:
Down you go, you scoundrel.

936
01:16:45,976 --> 01:16:47,932
Done!

937
01:16:54,151 --> 01:16:55,857
Yah!

938
01:17:05,871 --> 01:17:08,032
Hah!

939
01:17:12,795 --> 01:17:16,879
