953
01:20:54,933 --> 01:20:57,174
This is all my fault.

954
01:20:57,269 --> 01:20:59,260
I did this to you.

955
01:20:59,772 --> 01:21:01,262
To us.

956
01:21:07,571 --> 01:21:09,562
You've always been there for me.

957
01:21:10,949 --> 01:21:12,940
