973
01:22:52,217 --> 01:22:54,208
Oh! Mum.

974
01:22:57,222 --> 01:22:58,883
Eh?
I'm naked.

975
01:22:58,974 --> 01:23:01,215
Naked as a wee babby.

976
01:23:01,310 --> 01:23:03,392
