We will run and scream

990
01:24:05,207 --> 01:24:06,947
you will dance with me

991
01:24:07,042 --> 01:24:08,657
but how did this...

992
01:24:14,800 --> 01:24:18,292
Merida: There are those who say fate
is something beyond our command,

993
01:24:19,137 --> 01:24:21,674
that destiny is not our own.

994
01:24:22,182 --> 01:24:24,173
But I know better.

995
01:24:25,894 --> 01:24:28,385
Our fate lives within us.

996
01:24:30,232 --> 01:24:32,894
You only have to be brave enough
fo see it

997
01:24:40,492 --> 01:24:43,859
We will run and scream

998
01:24:43,954 --> 01:24:47,117
you will dance with me

999
01:24:47,457 --> 01:24:52,451
we'll fulfill our dreams
and we'll be free

